title: John Connolly -The Black Angel
description: When a young woman goes missing from the streets of New York, the abductors think that no one will go looking for her. They are wrong.... Charlie Parker and Louis are searching for her....Parker comes to realize that this disappearance is part of an older mystery linked to other dark deeds, and a mythical prize that has been sought for centuries :The Black Angel. But the Black Angel is not an object, it is not a myth, the Black Angel lives.
